'''competitor_speed''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

If [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Max no competitors|competitors]] are set to greater than zero then, competitor speed sets the speed at which the AI competitors will build.<br><br>
0 = very slow<br>
1 = slow<br>
2 = medium<br>
3 = fast<br>
4 = very fast<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
competitor_speed = 2
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 ]

'''Default:''' 2


